<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="towards-prep">towards <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tə'wɔːdz/    美 /tə'wɔːdz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>朝；向；面对：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She sat with her back towards the window. 
她背对窗户坐着。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She took my arm and we walked slowly towards the car.
她挽住我的胳膊，我们慢慢向车走去。</p><footer>2008 北京</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>针对；关于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>her attitude / feelings towards the comment 
她对此评论的态度/感受</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>接近：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Towards the end of the game she fell asleep. 
她在比赛快结束时睡着了。</p></div></div>